

'''Greenwashing''' (a portmanteau of "green" and "whitewash") is a term describing the deceptive use of [[green PR]] or [[green marketin]]g in order to promote a misleading perception that a company's policies or products (such as goods or services) are [[environmentally friendly]]. 

